Firayim Ministan Indiya zai halarci bikin gina haikalin a wurin da ake jayayya
NEW DELHI (AP) - Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin bude ginin wata mai gina gidan ibada na Hindu a wani yanki mai rikitarwa a arewacin Indiya inda masallacin karni na 16 da masu tsattsauran ra'ayi na Hindu suka rushe a shekarar 1992, a cewar kungiyar da ke kula da gina gidan ibada.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, ranar da masu shirya taron suka ce ta dace da Hindu a fannin taurari amma kuma wannan shekara ce da majalisar dokokin Indiya ta soke matsayin da ke da 'yancin kai na jiharta mai yawan musulmi, Jammu da Kashmir.
Ba za a iya rasa alamar ba ga magoya bayan da kuma abokan adawar Jam'iyyar Bharatiya Janata ta Modi, wato BJP, wadda ta yi shekaru da yawa tana da alkawuran kawar da 'yancin kai daga Kashmir da ke cike da tashin hankali da kuma gina haikali ga allahn Hindu Ram inda masallacin zamanin Mughal ya taɓa kasancewa, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh da masu bi suka yi imanin cewa shi ne wurin haihuwar Ram.
Saboda cutar korona har yanzu tana ta yaduwa a fadin Indiya, wacce ta ba da rahoton yawan mutane na uku mafi girma a duniya, za a watsa bikin kai tsaye a talabijin na jihar kuma za a iyakance yawan mahalarta da masu kallo, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kuma World Hindu Organization, ƙungiyar 'yan asalin Hindu da ke da alaƙa da BJP.
Haikalin zai zama "cibiyar dindindin da ba ta mutuwa ta jituwa ta zamantakewa, haɗin kai na ƙasa da haɗuwa da farkawa da jin daɗin Hindu, " ko kuma hanyar rayuwar Hindu, in ji kakakin ƙungiyar Vinod Bansal a cikin sanarwar labarai a ranar Asabar.
An warware wata takaddama da ta shafe shekaru 100 a kan wurin a shekarar da ta gabata bayan da jam'iyyar BJP ta lashe zaben kasar.
A watan Nuwamba, Kotun Koli ta yanke hukunci a madadin amincewar haikalin, ta ce za a ba da takardun neman Musulmi a kadada biyar a wani wuri na daban.
