Magajin garin Kansas City ya yi maraba da taimakon tarayya wajen magance kisan kai, amma yana damuwa game da dalilan Trump
Magajin garin Kansas City Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi game da dalilan da suka sa shugaban kasar Trump ya aika da 'yan sanda na tarayya zuwa biranen Amurka - yana cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimako wajen magance kisan kai a birnin Midwestern, yana ganin matakin zai iya zama game da karfafa damar sake zaben Trump.
"Na yi matukar takaici a wannan makon [da] shugaban ya ambaci zanga-zangar George Floyd, ya ambaci kungiyar Black Lives Matter, " in ji Lucas, dan Democrat, a "Fox News Sunday" na zanga-zangar kwanan nan game da rashin daidaito na launin fata da kuma zalunci na 'yan sanda.
"Ba haka yake ba a birnin Kansas City, muna da ƙaruwa a shekara bayan shekara, amma muna bukatar taimako don mu kawar da wasu kisan da ba a warware ba".
Lucas ya kara da cewa: "Bari mu yi kokarin samun hankali da kuma mayar da hankali kan warware kisan kai... Ina ganin idan ka saurari sanarwa na kwanan nan... muna farin cikin yin aiki tare da jami'an tarayya a cikin iyakance".
Duk da sonsa na samun jami'an tarayya su yi aiki tare da hukumomin da ke bin doka a yankin, Lucas ya ce jawabin Trump - musamman a cikin hasken rikici game da dabarun da jami'an tarayya ke amfani da su a Portland, Oregon - ya sa yawancin masu jefa kuri'arsa su nuna damuwa game da kasancewar jami'an a titunan birnin.
"Abin da ba mu bukata shi ne karin man fetur a kan wuta daga 'yan sandan tarayya don yin, ina ganin, wani ban sha'awa siyasa batun", ya ce.
Trump a ranar Laraba ya sanar da cewa zai tura jami'an tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen yaki da karuwar yawan wasu laifuka - wani mataki da ke nuna fadada shigar fadar Fadar White House a cikin hukumar kula da doka ta gida yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin shugaban "doka da tsari".
"Tashin" 'yan sanda da aka sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da sauran biranen Amurka wani ɓangare ne na Operation Legend - wanda aka sanya wa suna bayan LeGend Taliferro mai shekaru 4, wanda aka harbe shi da kisan kai yayin da yake barci a wani gida a Kansas City a ƙarshen watan da ya gabata.
Duk da yake aika da jami'an tarayya don taimakawa wajen bin doka a cikin gida ba sabon abu ba ne - Babban Lauyan Shari'a Bill Barr ya sanar da irin wannan yunƙurin a watan Disamba don birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - nau'in jami'an tarayya da ake aikawa, da wasu dabarun su, sun haifar da damuwa tsakanin 'yan majalisa na jihohi da na gida.
'Yan majalisa da dama daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana a kan gwamnatin Trump ta tura 'yan sandan zuwa garuruwan su, musamman bayan rahotanni cewa jami'an tarayya da ba a san su ba sun tsare masu zanga-zangar a Portland kuma sun kwashe su a cikin motocin da ba a sanya alamarsu ba.
Portland ta sha fama da zanga-zangar kusan kowace rana game da zalunci na 'yan sanda da nuna wariyar launin fata tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd yayin da yake tsare da 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga Mayu.
