Wani labarin Asabar na AP, babbar hukumar yada labarai ta Amurka, ya ce taron manema labarai na fadar White House na iya zama "tsararren al'ada", kamar yadda McEnany ya sanya su "tsabtace, cikakken tallace-tallace ga shugaban da ke fuskantar sake zaɓe, wurin kai hare-hare kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma dandalin tattaunawa mai sauƙi game da bayanai" game da abin da gwamnati ke yi.
